---
title: Dukkah Coated Duck with a Roasted Butternut Salad and Sumac Dressing
description: Tonight's dinner is a veritable explosion of colour and flavour. Sweet roasted butternut squash, peppery rocket, tangy sumac and salty feta make a bed for deliciously crispy-skinned duck. It's finished with dukkah, that gorgeous Middle Eastern mixture of roasted nuts and spices. Duck and dukkah, such a good combination it surely can't be a coincidence that their names are so similar?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/dukkah-crusted-duck-cca557c6-0ec58c43.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/dukkah-crusted-duck-59e9e8aa043c3c485d0e9f73-6e3bfc2f.pdf
